-box;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: bold;\">客户实践案例</span></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">企业级钉钉会话智能场景：基于 Tablestore（OTS）统一存储多轮对话长文本及其向量表示，支撑低延迟、个性化的 AI 助手服务，并高效提供对话记录查询与智能摘要生成能力。</span></p>\n   <div style=\"line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5527777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7b1cbd31&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmecoa.qpic.cn%2Fmmecoa_png%2FftnoqhiaHUy8aK9JzXchuKwYpHvYlicvqNsQXlXvaic8icH3BX8ficPq9ISpRfW7eEBUGpaC6tqaibfHVU6rVuu9c7QQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0%;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;min-width: 10%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;align-self: center;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"margin: -27px 0% -50px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:73px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">“</span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;flex: 100 100 0%;align-self: center;height: auto;border-left: 0px solid rgb(13, 39, 255);border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 4px;margin: 0