yle=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Tablestore 向量实例（含预建表结构）。</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">预集成 Dify 最新版 + Tablestore 插件。</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" start=\"3\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">启动服务 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ol>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">无需修改代码，系统自动识别。</span></p>\n    <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n    <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n    <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"ini\"><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">VECTOR_STORE</span>=tablestore&nbsp;</span></code></pre>\n    <p></p>\n    <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" start=\"4\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">创建知识库，体验混合检索 &nbsp;</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ol>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">导入文档后，向量与元数据自动写入 Tablestore；查询时自动执行高效混合检索。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">✅ 有了 OTS，你可以在不频繁折腾架构的前提下，更从容地面对数据增长。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">无需 Docker Compose 手动配置，无需 SDK 编码，真